metadata.name: LLB: PG Lion #1
metadata.description: Limitless Lions: Pre-Generation is an NFT collection created by Dr. Madness. The Pre-Generation is the preview collection of an NFT mega-project, the Limitless Lions, which is also being created by Dr. Madness. The Pre-Generation foreshadows the upcoming rise of the Limitless Lions, the actual main project, yet the Pre-Generation itself is still a highly special preview project, as a lot of time and effort was put into creating the one-of-a-kind concept project. The project started in July, 2022, as an interest to the metaverse and the digital world and an attempt to successfully achieve a major accomplishment in the fascinating universe of virtual and programmed creations. Dr. Madness created a huge variety of special layers before generating many unique digital collectibles for his first ever NFT collection, and listing them on OpenSea for an epic preview of the ultimate collection he is currently working on, and with the goal for it to become a huge hit of NFT and OpenSea history.
